      • findPendingAccountEntity

        public static PendingAccountEntity findPendingAccountEntity(com.google.appengine.api.datastore.DatastoreService datastore,
                                            com.google.appengine.api.datastore.Email emailAddress,
                                            java.lang.String password)
        Find a pending account entity with an optional password filter. If the filter is used (non-empty and non-null) then it will be used to find the pending account entity. Otherwise the matching pending account entity will be matched against the email only.
        Parameters:
        datastore - The datastore object used for the query.
        emailAddress - The email address to search for.
        password - The optional password associated with the account.
        Returns:
        A PendingAccountEntity with a non-null Entity object if the account was found.
